<BR>
NECROS ARE NOT OVERPOWERED - just smarter!!!<BR>
The class has a High Difficulty rating, tells you that when starting the character. I think Necros draw a certain type of player. Anyone can run up to a Orc and hit Auto-Attack. Necros use strategy and since we have a wide range of spells at our disposal, we have a wide range of strategies. Every time Verant has nerfed us, we have bounced back. Why? Because we use a different strategy. So now your thinking we have too many spells? Bah! Our strongest DOT takes 2 minutes to do full damage while a Wizard can do the same damage in 7 seconds. And a lot of our spells dont even work together. When 2 necros group there has to be a intensive cdiscussion first to see which necro is going to cast what spell, this is to ensure that neither Necro is wasting mana by cancelling the effect of the other. A lot of research and time goes into playing a necro, so before you complain about a class, at least play the class to a decent level so you know what your talking about.<BR>
<BR>
We arent too powerful, just misunderstood.<BR>
